{"type": "article", "id": 7768, "title": "GAP要改革，电子商务大势不可挡", "description": "难道未来实体店就只有展示厅的作用了吗", "date": "2015-03-25T16:21:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 358, "name": "电子商务"}, {"id": 548, "name": "快时尚"}, {"id": 2326, "name": "Gap"}], "category": 19, "author": 75588, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607163452YDo2cZL7XaEWRNBp.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t电子商务对服装品牌传统运营的冲击越来越大。日前，<span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">Gap </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">新上任的 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">CEO Art Peck </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">表示，未来 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">GAP </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">将进入 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">3.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">零售模式，重点发展品牌电子商务、移动端占有等一系列全渠道销售能力。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">Peck </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">表示，一旦具体的策略出台，将“不可避免”地关闭或者缩小一部分线下店铺。目前全球 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">GAP </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">零售店一共有 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">3680 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">家。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t“他想把移动端作为消费者交互的主要领地，不过他还不清楚要怎么去做。” 据 <span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">Fast Company </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">Danielle Sacks </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">说。但是他不会拒绝尝试一些新的手段，比如他提到的更新样衣间，手机注册，电子墙展示，服装的 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">RFID </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">识别技术等，甚至是 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">GAP </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的自动贩卖机。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t同时 <span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">Peck </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">意识到，一旦要在电子商户上和 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">ZARA</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">H&amp;M </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">较劲，就必须加快品牌的上新速度。目前，从开始设计到新品进店，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">GAP </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">所需要的时间是十个月，也就是 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">ZARA</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">H&amp;M </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的三倍。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">Peck </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">希望能够将这个周期压缩为 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">30 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">周。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">GAP </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">作为进入中国市场比较晚的高街品牌，在占领市场份额上比较吃亏。</span>快时尚品牌靠开店速度来扩张，仅去年第四季度，<span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">GAP </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">开新店 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">10 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">家，优衣库 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">32 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">家，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">H&amp;M 22 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">家，无印良品 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">14 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">家。这样做总收益是上去了，单店利润率却非常低。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">GAP </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">2015 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年第一季度的总收入比 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">2014 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年第四季度要高 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">7.36 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">亿元，但净利润率却下降了 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。同店收入销售收入比去年同期下降 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t无独有偶，<span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">American Apparel </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">CEO Paula Schneider </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">也表示，即将减少实体店铺的上货量，会将重心放在线上商店中，虽然这一向都没给品牌带来过太多利润。不过，他们已经聘请了首位数字商务首席官，来负责加强线上体验，一定程度上表示了他们的改革之心。</span>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}